      <h1 class='title'>EU Emissions Directive</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 cc1717-8WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_1717ws' title='Col. 1717WS &mdash; HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1717WS' name='column_1717ws' href='#column_1717ws' rel='bookmark'>1717WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_395'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-eric-illsley' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_395' title='Link to this speech by Mr Eric Illsley' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <span class='question_no'>12.</span>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-eric-illsley" title="Mr Eric Illsley">Mr. Illsley</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Secretary of State for Trade and Industry what steps she is taking to minimise any adverse impact of the EU Emissions Directive on industry. [189181]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_396'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-mike-obrien' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_396' title='Link to this speech by Mr Mike O'Brien' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-mike-obrien" title="Mr Mike O'Brien">Mr. Mike O'Brien</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">The EU emissions trading scheme is a cost effective and market friendly way of reducing CO<sub>2</sub> emissions. Industry's views have been taken at
          <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_1718ws' title='Col. 1718WS &mdash; HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1718WS' name='column_1718ws' href='#column_1718ws' rel='bookmark'>1718WS</a>
          every stage of the process; there have been five consultations so far. The plans for implementation are well developed and will be finalised shortly.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
